<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN""http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"> <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <head> <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/> <title>Customer Service Associate with 1 year and 4 months of experience in handling customer queries, resolving issues, and delivering quality support through calls and emails. Skilled in communication, problem-solving, andmaintaining customer satisfaction</title> </head> <body>   <div style="width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;padding:30px 45px;font-family:'Calibri';color:#7F7F7F;background-color:white"> <div style="width:100%;margin-bottom:25px;padding-bottom: 5px;"> <div> <div style="font-size:1.4em;margin-bottom:3px;font-weight:bold;">Amutha</div> <div>  Senior Customer Support Executive at Senior Customer Support Associate   </div> <div style="font-weight:bold;">    1y 4m | Chennai | 2 Lacs    </div> </div> <div style="text-align:right">  <div>7338972392</div>   <div>goodamutha@gmail.com</div>  </div> <div style="width:100%; height:1px; background-color: #d6d6d6; margin-top: 5px"> </div> </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:1.4em;">“</span> Customer Service Associate with 1 year and 4 months of experience in handling customer queries, resolving issues, and delivering quality support through calls and emails. Skilled in communication, problem-solving, andmaintaining customer satisfaction </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">WORK SUMMARY</div> <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> Senior Customer Service Associate with extensive experience in handling customer queries, resolving complaints, and delivering high-quality service across voice and non-voice processes. Skilled in managing escalations, maintaining SLA compliance, and ensuring customer satisfaction through effective communication and problem-solving. Experienced in CRM tools, ticketing systems, and cross-functional coordination. Known for strong interpersonal skills, process knowledge, and the ability to mentor junior team members while consistently meeting performance targets </div> <div>  <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;"><b>Industry : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">BPM / BPO</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;"><b>Functional Area : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Customer Success, Service & Operations</span> </div>   <div> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;"><b>Role : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Customer Success, Service & Operations - Other</span> </div>  </div> </div> <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">  <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">WORK EXPERIENCE</div>  <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> <div style="margin-bottom:3px;">  <span style="font-weight:bold;">Senior Customer Support Executive</span>   <span style="color:#A6A6A5;">Sep '24 - till date</span>  </div>  <div style="color:#4E81BD;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:3px;">Senior Customer Support Associate </div>   Senior customer support associate   </div>   <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">  </div> <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">  <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">EDUCATION DETAILS</div>  <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> <div>P.G.</div> <div> MBA/PGDM (Finance)  2024 </div> <div>Madras University, Chennai</div> </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> <div>P.G.</div> <div> MBA/PGDM (Finance)  2024 </div> <div>Madras University, Chennai</div> </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> <div>U.G.</div> <div> B.Com - Bachelor of Commerce (Commerce)  2022 </div> <div>Chellammal Women's College of Pachaiyappa's Trust, Chennai</div> </div>    </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <div style="font-weight:bold;top:30px;color:#F79647;">DESIRED JOB DETAILS</div> <div style="clear: both;display: table;">  <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;"><b>Job Type : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Permanent</span>  </div> <div style="clear: both;display: table;">  <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;"><b>Employment Status : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Full time</span>  </div> <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;"><b>US Work Status : </b></label>  <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Not Mentioned</span>  </div> <div style="clear: both;display: table;">  </div> <div style="clear: both;display: table;">  <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;"><b>Preferred Location : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Chennai</span>  </div> </div> <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">PERSONAL DETAILS</div>  <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;margin-right:15px;"><b>Name : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Amutha</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;margin-right:15px;"><b>Gender : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Female</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;margin-right:15px;"><b>Marital Status : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Single/unmarried</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;margin-right:15px;"><b>Date of Birth : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">18 Nov 2000</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;margin-right:15px;"><b>Address : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px"></span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;margin-right:15px;"><b>Mobile : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">7338972392(M)</span> </div>   <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;margin-bottom:3px;width:180px;display:inline-block;margin-right:15px;"><b>Email ID : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">goodamutha@gmail.com</span> </div>  </div>  </div> </div> </div>  <img src="" height="0px" width="0px"/>  </body> </html>